---
---
<section class="section testimonial">
  <div class="testimonial__inner" data-reveal>
    <blockquote class="testimonial__quote">
      „Cel mai bun lash artist din oraș. Gene impecabile, ședință relaxantă de
      fiecare dată."
    </blockquote>
    <p class="testimonial__author">
      — <strong>Andreea M.</strong>, clientă din 2023
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonial {
    padding: 5rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--plum);
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .testimonial__inner { max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .testimonial__quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.6vw, 2.6rem);
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .testimonial__author {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: color-mix(in oklab, var(--cream) 75%, transparent);
  }
  .testimonial__author strong { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; }

  @media (min-width: 768px) { .testimonial { padding: 7rem 2rem; } }
</style>
